                <h1>Optimize Your Mac: Control Background Apps</h1>
                <p>Mac background apps can silently consume system resources, impacting performance and battery life. It's essential to manage these apps, using Activity Monitor to identify and close unnecessary ones. Minimizing background apps ensures smoother operation, faster response times, and extends battery longevity, enhancing your overall macOS experience.</p>
